textBeforeTable: Sign up at the Aquatics Office from March 2–27. A meeting will take place on April 7 at 4:15pm. The race will be held on Saturday, May 30 at 10:00am. Join our annual spring Kid’s Triathlon Club to learn the competitive aspects of swimming, biking, running, and the transitions between each! Open to boys and girls ages 7–14 (must be in school).
